Text:
This is an incredibly gorgeous album, more similar to Felt Mountain than the two in between but perhaps not as dark. 

Thanks seventhtree for the preview. I will be spending my hard-earned on this for sure.
Very poor quality. Lots of popping and cracking in each file.

I just listened to this, no poor quality effects, in fact, Awesome audio! 

Def one of the best albums I have EVER heard. In the top 5, for sure. Get it!!!!!
